{"tid":713582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大新高壓政策：上莊要考牌，否則唔准借場","createTime":"2018-06-23T02:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T09:52:09.000Z","uid":63183,"like":20,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"bc8de51e9c319a1e2ef24055147b0a6ed0733e98","tid":713582,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/104744_bdb80901f4c763fe2833f40a93ec8a70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F104744_bdb80901f4c763fe2833f40a93ec8a70.jpg&h=8c98881b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上莊係大學生活一件大事，同學往往都可以透過服務自學到啲知識；不過，浸大高層似乎就唔係咁諗。你以為上莊，唔理校政就可以置身事外嗎？BU今年居然乘勢推出新政策：為咗逼學生讀名為「CODE[1]」嘅領袖課程，不惜以學會本有權利相脅。假若學會唔派代表出席CODE，將版禁止於七、八月借用學校場地，以及參與賣物周活動等。<br />\n<br />\n又鑒於今年為新政策過渡年，BU「蝗恩浩蕩」推出特赦措施。學生事務處公告咁講：「鑒於有一小撮學會向我哋就七、八月借用唔到場地向我哋求助，本處現提供以下補救措施：一、學會須提供悔過書（Confession）解釋為何唔去滿足要求；二、每缺席一個核心講座，學會須按Powerpoint撰寫不少於1,000字撮要交功課。」<br />\n<br />\n到底呢個反智嘅CODE如何冒出，由何人制定，山神就想請各方指教；起碼我幾年前上莊，未遇過咁荒唐嘅惡策。不過，此事足證浸大自從以鐵腕手段打壓抗議普通話同學後，高壓政策經已得勢不饒人，繼續擴張。校內同學必定會負隅頑抗；而即將放榜，未入校門嘅莘莘學子，則君子不立危牆之下，自己睇路喇。<br />\n<br />\n[1]全寫為「a series of workshops packaged as &ldquo;Coaching, Organization Development, and Engagement (CODE)&rdquo; Programme」<br />\n<br />\n附錄：學生事務處《CODE出席要求》信函<br />\n<br />\nDear Student Officers,<br />\n<br />\nRE: CODE Attendance Requirement<br />\n<br />\nThis May, a series of workshops packaged as &ldquo;Coaching, Organization Development, and Engagement (CODE)&rdquo; Programme, which provided tailor-made training for student officers, were conducted. Since the content of the two core seminars was considered essential to the development of student organizations, the attendance to the two core seminars was made as prerequisite for student organizations who have the need to (1) reserve venues via VFBS in July and August and (2) organize Sales Week in 2018-19.<br />\n<br />\nRecently, requests for help in venue reservation in July and August were received from a few student organizations which did not (or partially) fulfill the attendance requirement. Considering this is the first year to implement CODE with attendance requirements, the Office has resolved to offer remedial measures. Those student organizations who have not fulfilled CODE Attendance requirement would be required to send the following documents to sacla@hkbu.edu.hk on or before 22 June 2018 (Friday):<br />\n<br />\n1. A note to student organizations which have completed the CODE Programme, to explain with justifications or confession for not fulfilling the requirement; and<br />\n<br />\n2. A summary of no less than 1,000 words for EACH core seminar the student organization has missed. The Powerpoint slides could be viewed via the website (HKBU login required)<br />\n<br />\nCompleting the two documents with satisfactory level before the deadline would be regarded as completion of CODE requirement. Please note that no further arrangement would be provided for late submission. If your student organization were having a similar case, same measure would apply.<br />\n<br />\nKindly be advised that the remedial measure is offered to this transitional year only. Student organizations are recommended to ensure messages from the Office are well received and due action is taken.<br />\n<br />\nPlease contact Mr. Cliff WONG at 3411 2567 or via email cliffwong@hkbu.edu.hk for any queries.<br />\n<br />\nCampus Life and Amenities<br />\n<br />\nOffice of Student Affairs"},{"pid":"47e77becc8fca9946b1da4fc2dcff4857e43bb76","tid":713582,"uid":2419,"like":120,"dislike":3,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:50:07.000Z","msg":"雖然上莊好撚戇鳩 不過真係多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315f1f69a2f73bbaa534982a1efdfa45427993ba","tid":713582,"uid":65433,"like":7,"dislike":124,"score":-117,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:51:31.000Z","msg":"係就係家長式咗啲，但係咪因為以往浸大仔搞活動時無品同太多亂象先？"},{"pid":